01:17:11.640 --> 01:17:12.905
- Please, Michael.

01:17:12.905 --> 01:17:15.180
(coughing)

01:17:15.180 --> 01:17:16.013
- Sorry.

01:17:18.889 --> 01:17:22.056
(solemn choral music)

01:17:38.007 --> 01:17:40.410
- You didn't have to do it.

01:17:40.410 --> 01:17:41.743
- Relax, Vincent.

01:17:43.660 --> 01:17:44.493
