01:27:54.154 --> 01:27:56.904
(Mary screaming)

01:28:03.201 --> 01:28:05.868
(ominous music)

01:28:13.013 --> 01:28:13.846
- Michael.

01:28:36.381 --> 01:28:38.881
(eerie music)

01:28:45.378 --> 01:28:48.461
