01:30:25.750 --> 01:30:29.235
- No, you didn't, but your girlfriend did.

01:30:29.235 --> 01:30:31.170
(eerie music)

01:30:31.170 --> 01:30:32.970
- What happened here?

01:30:32.970 --> 01:30:34.270
