(moving to dramatic music)

01:38:03.704 --> 01:38:06.371
(somber music)

01:38:16.918 --> 01:38:17.751
(typewriter bell ringing)

01:38:17.751 --> 01:38:19.942
(roller clacking)

01:38:19.942 --> 01:38:22.609
(book thudding)
